        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When no expedited processing options are available for a permit or application, clearly state this to the user :

There is no way to expedite an application. Applications generally process in 7 to 10 
business days. A complete packet is required in order to obtain an ABC permit. An 
application for permit can be delayed for incomplete information; local government 
objection to the application or to the applicant(s); or for lack of cooperation by the 
applicant(s) with the Commission and with the Alcohol Law Enforcement (ALE) agents.</description>
